"This paper is structured as follows. In Section 2 we dis-
cuss the geometry of eccentric discs and restate the coor-
dinate system of Ogilvie & Lynch (2019). In Section 3 we
derive the equations for the dynamical vertical structure, in-
cluding the effects of a Maxwell stress, in this coordinate sys-
