and a coherent magnetic field which obeys the ideal induc-
tion equation. In Section 5 we consider a nonlinear consti-
tutive model for the magnetic field. In our discussion we
discuss the stability of our solutions (Section 6.1) and the"
"possibility of dynamo action in the disc (6.2). We present
our conclusions in Section 7 and additional mathematical
details are in the appendices."
